Lokhu kuvezwe ngamaphoyisa kaMasipala waseTshwane Metro Police Department (TMPD) ngemuva komkhankaso wokulwa nabashayela bephuzile. “Amaphoyisa aseTshwane, esebenzisana nezinye izinhlaka, enze umkhankaso ngoMgqibelo ebusuku lapho ebophe khona abebeshayela bephuzile eHatfield,” kusho uSenior Superintendent Isaac Mahamba, okhulumela amaphoyisa kamasipala. Uthe bangu-15 abantu ababoshiwe phakathi kuka-10 no-12 ebusuku. “Omunye wabantu ababoshiwe umdlali weBafana ona-28. Lo mdlali wayedlalela i-Orlando Pirates.” UMahamba uthe ukushayela uphuzile ngenye yezinto ezidala izingozi kulo mkhandlu. “Noma ngubani otholakala ephuzile uzoboshwa. Sizoqhubeka nemikhankaso efuze le ngoba ngeke sibabekezelele abantu ababeka abanye engcupheni.” Ugqugquzele abashayeli ukuthi benze ezinye izinhlelo ukuze bafike emakhaya kunokushayela bephuzile. “Akekho umuntu ongaphezu komthetho. Siwashayela ihlombe amaphoyisa ngomsebenzi wawo,” kusho uMahamba.